[
    {
        "text": "Hayao Miyazaki was born in Tokyo on January 5, 1941.",
        "startTime": 2833,
        "endTime": 7717,
        "slowStartTime": 4400,
        "slowEndTime": 11800
    },
    {
        "text": "As a boy, he liked to read and draw cartoons.",
        "startTime": 8267,
        "endTime": 11317,
        "slowStartTime": 12550,
        "slowEndTime": 17200
    },
    {
        "text": "After graduating from university in 1963, Miyazaki joined the Toei Animation Company.",
        "startTime": 11900,
        "endTime": 18350,
        "slowStartTime": 18000,
        "slowEndTime": 27750
    },
    {
        "text": "At Toei, he worked on many animated movies like the famous \"Puss in Boots\".",
        "startTime": 19100,
        "endTime": 24217,
        "slowStartTime": 28800,
        "slowEndTime": 36550
    },
    {
        "text": "In 1984, he made \"Nausicaa of the Valley of the Wind\",...",
        "startTime": 24833,
        "endTime": 28450,
        "slowStartTime": 37400,
        "slowEndTime": 42900
    },
    {
        "text": "...which was based on a comic book he wrote.",
        "startTime": 28833,
        "endTime": 30750,
        "slowStartTime": 43400,
        "slowEndTime": 46350
    },
    {
        "text": "Because this movie was so successful,...",
        "startTime": 31300,
        "endTime": 33383,
        "slowStartTime": 47100,
        "slowEndTime": 50300
    },
    {
        "text": "...Miyazaki was able to start his own animation company, Studio Ghibli.",
        "startTime": 33767,
        "endTime": 38383,
        "slowStartTime": 50800,
        "slowEndTime": 57800
    },
    {
        "text": "One of Miyazaki's most loved movies is \"My Neighbor Totoro\", made in 1987.",
        "startTime": 39200,
        "endTime": 44916,
        "slowStartTime": 58950,
        "slowEndTime": 67599
    },
    {
        "text": "It is a children's movie, but many adults like it too.",
        "startTime": 45466,
        "endTime": 48850,
        "slowStartTime": 68349,
        "slowEndTime": 73500
    },
    {
        "text": "The movie is about two sisters...",
        "startTime": 49567,
        "endTime": 51401,
        "slowStartTime": 74500,
        "slowEndTime": 77327
    },
    {
        "text": "...who become friends with an enormous, supernatural animal named Totoro.",
        "startTime": 51542,
        "endTime": 55850,
        "slowStartTime": 77463,
        "slowEndTime": 84000
    },
    {
        "text": "It is a very warmhearted story...",
        "startTime": 56533,
        "endTime": 58617,
        "slowStartTime": 84950,
        "slowEndTime": 88150
    },
    {
        "text": "...with many fantastic characters such as Cat Bus, a cat that is also a bus.",
        "startTime": 58933,
        "endTime": 64450,
        "slowStartTime": 88550,
        "slowEndTime": 96900
    },
    {
        "text": "Miyazaki's 2001 movie, \"Spirited Away\", was even more popular than \"Totoro\".",
        "startTime": 65133,
        "endTime": 70783,
        "slowStartTime": 97850,
        "slowEndTime": 106400
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, it made more money than any other movie in Japanese history.",
        "startTime": 71367,
        "endTime": 75683,
        "slowStartTime": 107200,
        "slowEndTime": 113750
    },
    {
        "text": "All of Miyazaki's movies contain strange but charming people and creatures.",
        "startTime": 76567,
        "endTime": 81483,
        "slowStartTime": 115000,
        "slowEndTime": 122450
    },
    {
        "text": "Many of his stories happen in worlds that are different from ours.",
        "startTime": 82033,
        "endTime": 85450,
        "slowStartTime": 123200,
        "slowEndTime": 128400
    },
    {
        "text": "However, they still show his ideas about real life.",
        "startTime": 86033,
        "endTime": 89250,
        "slowStartTime": 129199,
        "slowEndTime": 134100
    },
    {
        "text": "He often points out how humans hurt the natural world.",
        "startTime": 89967,
        "endTime": 93050,
        "slowStartTime": 135100,
        "slowEndTime": 139800
    },
    {
        "text": "He thinks people should change how they live.",
        "startTime": 93700,
        "endTime": 95850,
        "slowStartTime": 140700,
        "slowEndTime": 144000
    },
    {
        "text": "Miyazaki's movies combine fantasy and reality in an original way.",
        "startTime": 96633,
        "endTime": 101383,
        "slowStartTime": 145100,
        "slowEndTime": 152300
    },
    {
        "text": "This may be why so many people like his movies.",
        "startTime": 102067,
        "endTime": 105117,
        "slowStartTime": 153250,
        "slowEndTime": 157900
    }
]